| pages = 32
}}</ref> Bengali words are currently Romanized on Wikipedia using a [[phonemic orthography|phonemic transcription]], where the pronunciation is represented with no reference to the spelling. The Wikipedia Romanization is given in the table below, with [[International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] transcriptions found under the heading "Sounds".

