==Sounds==
{{main|Bengali phonology}}
The [[phoneme|phonemic]] inventory of Bengali consists of 29 consonants and 14 vowels, including the seven [[nasalization|nasalized vowels]]. An approximate [[phonetics|phonetic]] scheme is set out below in [[International Phonetic Alphabet]].

